  <div>
    <p>Dogs: The Nose Knows</p>
    <p>Article by Doug Dachshund (2002/12/03)</p>
    <p>Summary: Though published in 2002, this publication is still the go-to resource concerning canine's seemingly super-natural sensing abilities. In it, Doug categorizes these abilities, asserts and explains how they are not super-natural, and how they are observed to change from breed to breed.</p>
    <p><a href="DDachshund2002.pdf">Read the complete article here</a></p>
