    <p>Mice: More Intelligent that You Might Think</p>
    <p>Article by Michela Meeker (2023/11/17)</p>
    <p>Summary: Behold the lowly mouse! Long maligned as a scourge of humanity's existence. However, in her most recent publication, Michela Meeker takes the reader on a historical journey to uncover the true nature of mice - their behavior, their motivations, and their effect on humanity through the ages.</p>
    <p><a href="MMeeker2023.pdf">Read the complete article here</a></p>
